snippet.title: Stunt Driver gameplay (PC Game, 1990)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Stunt Driver (aka crash course), Dos PC game produced by Sphere in 1990 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/stunt-driver/15906/
Stunt Driver is a very nice game, arcade race, controls are quite simple and very easy car to drive, is quite interesting races.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
International Moto X - https://youtu.be/QJW84neJeS8
Stunt Island - https://youtu.be/2vqBu3EgZTM
Chicago 90 - https://youtu.be/0c7TqD-hAGw
